<TITLE> Orion chairman Obaidul Karim jailed </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, June 25 (bdnews24.com)  A special court Wednesday sentenced Orion Group chairman Obaidul Karim to 13 years in prison in a graft case, filed by the Anticorruption Commission. Judge Khandaker Kamal Uzzaman of the Special Court-9 on the Jatiya Sangsad complex also fined Obaidul Tk 10 lakh and ordered one more year in jail in failure to pay the fine. The court also ordered confiscation of Obaidul's Tk 50.92 crore worth of property earned by illegal means. The convict was on the run. bdnew
